id.description: The unique identifier for this relationship.

version.description:
Version number used for optimistic concurrency.  Automatically managed by the system.

Updating an Obj with a null or 0 value for version will cause the concurrency check to be skipped and should only
be done with great caution.

typeWithBindings.description: Persists concrete type with bindings for generic types where instance has parameter bindings

start.description: The start datetime when this bulb was installed in the fixture.

end.description: The end datetime when this bulb was removed from the fixture.

title:
Represents the relationship between a SmartBulb and a Fixture over a time period.
Tracks which bulb was installed in which fixture and when.
name: SmartBulbToFixtureRelation
